subproject.corporate outcome: National, regional and local levels of governance expand their capacities to manage the equitable delivery of public services
subproject.description: The project aims to improve the standards of local electoral practices and change deeply-rooted cultural practices by provision of civic education to rural women and future voters on their rights and obligations and the election procedure.
